<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ms">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Undangan Pernikahan Diraja</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts untuk Tipografi yang Mewah -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Great+Vibes&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome untuk Ikon Sosial & RSVP -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        /* --- CSS VANILA --- */
        :root {
            --primary: #c5a880; /* Champagne Gold */
            --primary-dark: #a3845b;
            --secondary: #e6dfd3;
            --dark: #2c261e;
            --light: #fdfbf7;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(44, 38, 30, 0.08);
            --transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, .brand {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .cursive {
            font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            line-height: 1.2;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        }

        /* Pembuka Tirai / Splash Screen */
        #splash {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #fdfbf7 0%, #f4eee1 100%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 9999;
            transition: opacity 1s ease, transform 1s ease;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        #splash.fade-out {
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .splash-card {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 50% 50% 0 0;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            animation: pulse 3s infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: translateY(0); }
            100% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        /* Hiasan Bucu (Border Corner) */
        .corner-decoration {
            position: absolute;
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .top-left { top: 15px; left: 15px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; }
        .top-right { top: 15px; right: 15px; border-left: none; border-bottom: none; }
        .bottom-left { bottom: 15px; left: 15px; border-right: none; border-top: none; }
        .bottom-right { bottom: 15px; right: 15px; border-left: none; border-top: none; }

        .btn-open {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 12px 35px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: var(--white);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(197, 168, 128, 0.4);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-open:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(197, 168, 128, 0.6);
        }

        /* Pemain Audio */
        .music-control {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 25px;
            right: 25px;
            background: var(--white);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary);
            width: 45px;
            height: 45px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 999;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .music-control:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .music-control i {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .music-control.playing i {
            animation: rotateMusic 4s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotateMusic {
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* Hiasan Floral SVG */
        .floral-header {
            width: 150px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* Bahagian Utama (Main Sections) */
        section {
            padding: 100px 20px;
            min-height: 80vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Latar belakang lembut dengan corak hiasan */
        .bg-pattern {
            background-image: radial-gradient(var(--secondary) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            background-color: var(--light);
        }

        .bg-white {
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Kesan Tatalan (Scroll Animations) */
        .fade-in-up {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(40px);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .fade-in-up.appear {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* 1. Hero Section */
        #hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.9), rgba(253, 251, 247, 0.95)),
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .couple-names {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .couple-names span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
        }

        .hero-date {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--primary);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 10px 0;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
        }

        /* 2. Mukaddimah Section */
        #muqaddimah {
            background: var(--white);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary);
        }

        .bismillah {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        .salutation {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .parents-names {
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        /* 3. Pengantin Section */
        #pengantin {
            background-color: var(--light);
        }

        .bride-groom-card {
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px 25px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin: 30px 0;
            border: 1px solid rgba(197, 168, 128, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .bride-groom-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .ampersand {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        /* 4. Butiran Majlis */
        #butiran {
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        .event-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .event-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .event-card {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--secondary);
            text-align: left;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .event-card h3 {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary);
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .info-item i {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-right: 15px;
            margin-top: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* Atur Cara Senarai */
        .timeline {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 20px;
            border-left: 2px solid var(--primary);
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .timeline-item::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -17px;
            top: 6px;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background: var(--primary-dark);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* 5. Countdown Section */
        #countdown-sec {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(44, 38, 30, 0.85), rgba(44, 38, 30, 0.9)),
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511285560929-80b456fea0bc?q=80&w=2069&auto=format&fit=crop');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: var(--white);
        }

        #countdown-sec h2 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .timer-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .time-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            min-width: 90px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .time-box span {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            display: block;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .time-box label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* 6. Quran Verse & Quote Section */
        #doa {
            background-color: var(--white);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .prayer-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 2;
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: #555;
        }

        .quote-signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        /* 7. RSVP & Lokasi Section */
        #rsvp-lokasi {
            background-color: var(--light);
        }

        .rsvp-form-container {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            border: 1px solid var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(197, 168, 128, 0.3);
        }

        .radio-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .radio-option {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
            color: var(--white);
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            transition: var(--transition);
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background-color: var(--dark);
        }

        /* Butang Lokasi & Hubungi */
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .btn-action {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: var(--white);
            color: var(--dark);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .btn-action:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: var(--white);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-action.primary {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .btn-action.primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
        }

        /* Notifikasi Tersuai (Custom Toast Notification) */
        #toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(100px);
            background-color: var(--dark);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            z-index: 10000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        #toast.show {
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--dark);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        footer a {
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Responsif untuk Skrin Kecil */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .cursive { font-size: 2.3rem; }
            .couple-names span { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            section { padding: 70px 15px; }
            .timer-container { gap: 10px; }
            .time-box { min-width: 70px; padding: 10px; }
            .time-box span { font-size: 1.6rem; }
            .rsvp-form-container { padding: 25px 15px; }
            .btn-action { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- PEMBUKA TIRAI (SPLASH SCREEN) -->
    <div id="splash">
        <div class="splash-card">
            <div class="corner-decoration top-left"></div>
            <div class="corner-decoration top-right"></div>
            <div class="corner-decoration bottom-left"></div>
            <div class="corner-decoration bottom-right"></div>
            
            <p class="hero-title" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Walimatulurus</p>
            <h1 class="cursive" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Afiqah & Haziq</h1>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #777;">SABTU, 12 SEPTEMBER 2026</p>
            
            <button class="btn-open" onclick="bukaUndangan()">
                <i class="fa-solid rel fa-envelope-open" style="margin-right: 8px;"></i> Buka Undangan
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BUTANG KAWALAN MUZIK (BACKING AUDIO) -->
    <div class="music-control" id="musicBtn" onclick="toggleMuzik()">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-music"></i>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Audio Fail (Menggunakan Lagu Instrumental yang Bebas Royalti / Lembut) -->
    <audio id="bgMusic" loop>
        <source src="https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-1.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
    </audio>

    <!-- 1. HERO SECTION -->
    <section id="hero" class="bg-pattern">
        <div class="container fade-in-up">
            <!-- Hiasan Atas -->
            <svg class="floral-header" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <path d="M50 10 C 35 30, 20 40, 50 90 C 80 40, 65 30, 50 10 Z" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="#c5a880"/>
                <path d="M50 30 C 40 45, 35 50, 50 75 C 65 50, 60 45, 50 30 Z" stroke-width="1" stroke="#a3845b"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="hero-title">Undangan Perkahwinan</p>
            <div class="couple-names">
                <span class="cursive">Afiqah Puteri</span>
                <div class="ampersand">&amp;</div>
                <span class="cursive">Haziq Putra</span>
            </div>
            <p class="hero-date">SABTU | 12 SEPTEMBER 2026</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. MUQADDIMAH & JEMPUTAN -->
    <section id="muqaddimah">
        <div class="container fade-in-up">
            <p class="bismillah">بِسْمِ اللهِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِيْم</p>
            <p class="salutation">Assalamualaikum Warahmatullahi Wabarakatuh</p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 25px;">Dengan penuh kesyukuran ke hadrat Allah SWT serta memohon keberkatan-Nya, kami:</p>
            
            <p class="parents-names">Encik Ahmad bin Sulaiman & Puan Aminah binti Yusuf</p>
            
            <p style="margin: 25px auto; max-width: 600px;">
                dengan segala hormatnya menjemput Dato' / Datin / Tuan / Puan / Encik / Cik serta seisi keluarga ke majlis perkahwinan anakanda kami:
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. PENGANTIN SECTION -->
    <section id="pengantin">
        <div class="container fade-in-up">
            <svg class="floral-header" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none">
                <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="30" stroke="#c5a880" stroke-width="1"/>
                <path d="M50 10 Q 50 40 30 50 Q 50 60 50 90" stroke="#a3845b" stroke-width="1.5"/>
            </svg>
            
            <div class="bride-groom-card">
                <h2 class="cursive">Nur Afiqah Binti Ahmad</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #777; margin-top: 10px;">
                    Puteri kepada Encik Ahmad bin Sulaiman & Puan Aminah binti Yusuf
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="ampersand">dengan</div>

            <div class="bride-groom-card">
                <h2 class="cursive">Mohamad Haziq Bin Ramli</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #777; margin-top: 10px;">
                    Putera kepada Encik Ramli bin Kassim & Puan Rosnah binti Osman
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 4. BUTIRAN MAJLIS & ATUR CARA -->
    <section id="butiran">
        <div class="container fade-in-up">
            <h2 style="color: var(--primary-dark); font-weight: 600;">Butiran Majlis</h2>
            <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 20px;">Segala maklumat penting berkaitan majlis perkahwinan kami.</p>

            <div class="event-grid">
                <!-- Kad Lokasi & Tarikh -->
                <div class="event-card">
                    <h3>Tarikh & Tempat</h3>
                    <div class="info-item" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-days"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Hari & Tarikh</strong>
                            <p>Sabtu, 12 September 2026</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Waktu Majlis</strong>
                            <p>11:00 Pagi - 4:00 Petang</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Lokasi</strong>
                            <p>Dewan Banquet Seri Anggerik, Jalan Permaisuri 5, Bukit Antarabangsa, 68000 Ampang, Selangor</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Kad Atur Cara -->
                <div class="event-card">
                    <h3>Atur Cara Majlis</h3>
                    <ul class="timeline">
                        <li class="timeline-item">
                            <strong>11:00 Pagi</strong>
                            <p>Ketibaan para tetamu & jamuan makan bermula</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-item">
                            <strong>12:45 Tengah Hari</strong>
                            <p>Ketibaan Pengantin Diraja (Acara Bersanding)</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-item">
                            <strong>1:15 Tengah Hari</strong>
                            <p>Makan Beradab & Memotong Kek Perkahwinan</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="timeline-item">
                            <strong>4:00 Petang</strong>
                            <p>Majlis Bersurai</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. COUNTDOWN TIMER -->
    <section id="countdown-sec">
        <div class="container fade-in-up">
            <h2>Menanti Hari Bahagia</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Kami sedang mengira hari untuk disatukan:</p>
            <div class="timer-container">
                <div class="time-box">
                    <span id="days">00</span>
                    <label>Hari</label>
                </div>
                <div class="time-box">
                    <span id="hours">00</span>
                    <label>Jam</label>
                </div>
                <div class="time-box">
                    <span id="minutes">00</span>
                    <label>Minit</label>
                </div>
                <div class="time-box">
                    <span id="seconds">00</span>
                    <label>Saat</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. PRAYER & QUOTE -->
    <section id="doa" class="bg-pattern">
        <div class="container fade-in-up">
            <p class="prayer-text">
                "Ya Allah, himpunkanlah antara kedua-duanya dengan kebaikan, satukanlah hati mereka dalam ketaatan kepada-Mu dan kurniakanlah kebahagiaan serta keberkatan dalam kehidupan mereka."
            </p>
            <div class="quote-signature">
                "Raja Sehari, Seikhlas Hati Menyambut Tetamu"
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555;">
                Kehadiran dan doa restu Tuan / Puan amat kami hargai dan dahului dengan ucapan terima kasih.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

